{"tid":1809193,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"人民日報認證：黃色經濟圈大有作為","createTime":"2020-01-03T02:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T05:16:37.000Z","uid":156878,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"13c37e23f827f34b6ac528d5356babf0dd58bc07","tid":1809193,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:15:20.000Z","msg":"人民日報發表文章，認為所謂「黃色經濟圈」注定是一個笑話。<br />\n文章說，黃色經濟圈剝奪市民消費選擇的自由，亦損傷市民經營活動的自由，在商界刮起黑色恐怖之風，黃色經濟圈只是幌子，只是排除異己的手段，批評反中亂港分子想要的只是「攬炒」，是香港經濟的衰敗、社會文明的崩塌、法治精神的潰敗。"},{"pid":"deaa3a2cb6e8441242e51b48dd77a767a2f845ab","tid":1809193,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:15:37.000Z","msg":"踏入2020 年，捉鬼成為左抗爭面對嘅首個危機，而呢個危機係致命嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809084</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f1dcf3f7a669b293e23997749ef4901d6beaa8e4","tid":1809193,"uid":284104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:21:18.000Z","msg":"剝奪自由選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂其實你可以自由選擇食美心飲 Starbucks<br />\n唔會比人打架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69aa91215a648391b35823af793ccf89f6b5a64b","tid":1809193,"uid":8049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:13:51.000Z","msg":"我們都有一個夢想<br />\n<br />\n穩固黃色經濟圈成型 新系統迎接新模式<br />\n<br />\n抵制支付寶來襲，抗衡八達通賣港<br />\n<br />\n屬於我地新時代既支付系統。<br />\n[招兵買馬] <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1805119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1805119</a><br />\n[關注我們] <a href=\"https://t.me/TimesPayHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTimesPayHK&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7BckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=12aeaf78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TimesPayHK</a>"},{"pid":"f8e84c7e2a08a59a3a1d51733a13f7fe66597ddf","tid":1809193,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"<strong>注定是